text: The Harvest Month () is a 1956 Finnish drama movie directed by Matti Kassila and starring Toivo Mäkelä, Emma Väänänen, Rauni Luoma, Aino-Maija Tikkanen, Rauni Ikäheimo, Senni Nieminen, Heikki Savolainen, Sylvi Salonen, Olavi Ahonen. ==Other websites== * Category:1956 drama movies Category:Finnish movies Category:Movies directed by Matti Kassila
title: The Harvest Month
